<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="everywhere-adv">everywhere <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'evriweə(r)/    美 /'evriwer/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>到处；无论何处：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The state of our parks is very shocking, with rubbish everywhere. 
我们公园的状况很令人震惊，到处都是垃圾。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>"Teamworking" is found everywhere within just about every organization.
“团队合作”几乎在每个组织内都存在。</p><footer>2011 浙江</footer></div>

<p>注: everywhere可引导地点状语从句。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My dog followed me everywhere I went. 无论我走到哪里，我的狗都跟着我。
</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>There were piles of newspapers <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(到处) in the house.  （2007 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. everywhere  </p></div>